scron - simple cron daemon
==========================

features
--------
schedule tasks
single daemon, config and initscript
log job output: command &>> /var/log/cron.log
run as different user: su -c 'command' user
log to stdout and syslog
no mail support

usage
-----
usage: crond [options]
-h        help
-d        daemon
-f <file> config file

example config
--------------
# tm_min, tm_hour, tm_mday, tm_mon, tm_wday, command
0	6	*	*	*	updatedb	# 06:00 every day
30	5	*	*	1-5	emerge --sync	# 5:30 every weekday
